// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-0019 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: 61be7744-fec0-5564-ae7f-8628d19d0e89

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.10*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:13.04*")
